12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
14 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4675 of Title 70, unless there
15 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
16 A. Beginning on the effective date of this act and ending five
17 (5) academic years thereafter, there is hereby declared a moratorium
18 on the following higher education course and program restrictions:
19 1. Northern Oklahoma College's exclusive authority to offer all
20 lower division courses and programs at the University Center at
21 Ponca City as provided by subsection B of Section 3213.1 of this
22 title;
